		<hr size="1">My advice to a new wizard....</P><P>1. Study up our your class's abilities, spells, etc.<BR>2. Try to get your newbie armor, even though it really isn't that good.<BR>3. Practice all your spell types as much as possible, even conjuring.<BR>4. Don't worry about melee skills, but you should try to keep your defence skill up.</P><P>If I think of more, I will add them on later.</P><P>Good luck and welcome.</P><P><BR>Wizard of the 57th Circle of Knowledge.<BR>Bard of the 51st silly song.<BR>Beasty of the 25th soloing level.<BR>Shadow Knight of the 8th level of Evil.<BR>12th level maker of viscous mana (Enchanter)</P><P>"There is always one more imbecile than you had planned for."<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
