		<hr size="1">The most important thing to learn is how to balance your agro! Learn that and groups will be more likely to accept you. Nothing worse then hearing from my tank friends about this lame wizard they grouped with who over nuke and yell at the tanks for not taunting. So do yourself a favor friend learn agro management. It's a key skill if you ever plan on reaching then end game.</P><P><font size=+2 face="Impact" color="blue"><i>Azurewrath Mythryn</i></font><br><font size=+1 face="chiller" color="red">Arcanist of Solusek Ro</font><br>Vallon Zek <br><blockquote><i>"A wizard is never late, nor is he ever early. He arrives precisely when he means to"<br>         -Gandalf Stormcrow<i></hr></blockquote><br></P><P><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
